Introduction
------------

This piece of software is the configuration library for the satellite
emulation testbed OpenSAND

License
-------

see COPYING


Library
-------

The sources are in the src subdirectory. The sources build a library
that allow OpenSAND configuration files parsing. See the INSTALL file to
learn how to build the libraries.
To compile an application using the OpenSAND configuration library use the
following expression:
g++ `pkg-config opensand_conf --cflags` myappli.cpp `pkg-config opensand_conf --libs` -o myappli


